00:24:48.615 --> 00:24:50.490
dense cities of course.

00:24:50.490 --> 00:24:51.670
How do they move people in?

00:24:51.670 --> 00:24:53.604
Like do they have BRT systems?

00:24:53.604 --> 00:24:55.020
PROFESSOR: Yeah,
