[INTERPOSING VOICES]

00:26:25.730 --> 00:26:27.210
PROFESSOR: Yeah, but they're
not currently operating.

00:26:27.210 --> 00:26:27.830
AUDIENCE: You would
see [INAUDIBLE]..

00:26:27.830 --> 00:26:29.210
PROFESSOR: Yeah,
so that's right.

00:26:29.210 --> 00:26:30.420
So that's another good point.

00:26:30.420 --> 00:26:32.810
So if we included things
that were operating

00:26:32.810 --> 00:26:35.510
and no longer dropped,
