00:49:43.600 --> 00:49:44.410
the locomotives.

00:49:44.410 --> 00:49:48.690
You have the attendants
looking at tickets.

00:49:48.690 --> 00:49:52.960
You have rail to maintain
and stations to maintain.

00:49:52.960 --> 00:49:54.600
So that's commuter rail.

00:49:54.600 --> 00:49:56.490
Heavy rail is 5.5.

00:49:56.490 --> 00:49:59.470
Again, it starts
early, runs late.

00:49:59.470 --> 00:50:02.580
You have a lot of stations to
maintain, more so than commuter

00:50:02.580 --> 00:50:07.020
rail, so 5.5.

00:50:07.020 --> 00:50:08.370
